prior_art_claims.claim:
RESP2 encodes null as a null bulk string ($-1
) or null array (*-1
); RESP3 adds a dedicated null type (_
). Clients must distinguish null array vs empty array (*0).

verification.note:
Protocol spec confirms RESP2 null bulk string ($-1
) and null array (*-1
), and RESP3 dedicated null type (_
). Confirmed.
